hadiths[34]{hadithnumber,text}:
2351,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein doodh aur pani ka aik piyala pesh kya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko piyaa . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki daain taraf aik nau-umr ladka betha hua tha aur kuchh badey boodhey log baain taraf baithey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ladkey ! kya to ijazat dega ke main pahley ye piyala badon ko de dun. is par us ne kaha, ya Rasulullah ! main to aap ke jhootey mein se apne hisse ko apne siwa kisi ko nahi de sakta. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo piyala pahley usi ko de diya."
2352,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ghar mein pali hui aik bakri ka doodh dohaa gaya, jo Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) hi ke ghar mein pali thi. phir iske doodh mein us kuwein ka pani mila kar jo Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein iska piyala pesh kya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey piyaa . jab apne munh se piyala aap ne juda kya to baain taraf Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they aur daain taraf aik dehati tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) darey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye piyala dehati ko na de dein. isliye unhon-ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko de dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyala usi dehati ko diya jo aap ki daain taraf tha aur farmaya ke daain taraf wala zyada haqdaar hai. phir wo jo uski dahini taraf ho."
2353,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya bachchey huey pani se kisi ko isliye na rokaa jaey ke is tarah jo zarurat se zyada ghaas ho wo bhi ruki rahe.
2354,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya faaltu pani se kisi ko us gharaz se na roko ke jo ghaas zarurat se zyada ho usey bhi rok lo.
2355,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kaan (main marney waale) ka taawaan nahi, kuwein (main gir kar mar janey waale) ka taawaan nahi. aur kisi ka janwar (agar kisi aadmi ko maarey to uska ( taawaan nahi. garhey huey maal mein se panchwan hissey dena hoga."
2356,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs koi aisi jhooti qism khaaey jiske zariey wo kisi musalman ke maal par nahaq qabza kar ley to wo Allah se us haal mein milega ke Allah Taala is par bahut zyada ghazab naak hoga aur phir Allah Taala ne ( sura Aale-Imran ki ye ( aayat nazil farmai ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ke zariey duniya ki thodi daulat khareedtey hain'' aakhir aayat tak. phir Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur puchha ke abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne tum se kya hadis bayan ki hai? ye aayat to mere barey mein nazil hui thi. mera aik kunwaan mere chacha zaad bhai ki zameen mein tha. ( phir jhagdaa hua to ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke to apne gawah la . maine arz kya ke gawah to mere paas nahi hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir fareeq mukhalif se qism ley ley. is par maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! ye to qism kha baithey ga . ye sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya aur Allah Taala ne bhi us barey mein ye aayat nazil farma kar uski tasdeeq ki.
2357,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs koi aisi jhooti qism khaaey jiske zariey wo kisi musalman ke maal par nahaq qabza kar ley to wo Allah se us haal mein milega ke Allah Taala is par bahut zyada ghazab naak hoga aur phir Allah Taala ne ( sura Aale-Imran ki ye ( aayat nazil farmai ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ke zariey duniya ki thodi daulat khareedtey hain'' aakhir aayat tak. phir Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur puchha ke abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne tum se kya hadis bayan ki hai? ye aayat to mere barey mein nazil hui thi. mera aik kunwaan mere chacha zaad bhai ki zameen mein tha. ( phir jhagdaa hua to ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke to apne gawah la . maine arz kya ke gawah to mere paas nahi hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir fareeq mukhalif se qism ley ley. is par maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! ye to qism kha baithey ga . ye sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya aur Allah Taala ne bhi us barey mein ye aayat nazil farma kar uski tasdeeq ki.
2358,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya teen tarah ke log wo hongey jinki taraf qiyamat ke din Allah Taala nazar bhi nahi uthaaeyga aur na unhein paak karega, balke unke liye dardnak azab hoga. aik wo shakhs jiske paas rastey mein zarurat se zyada pani ho aur us ne kisi musaafir ko iske istemal se rok diya. doosra wo shakhs jo kisi Hakim se bait sirf duniya ke liye karey ke agar wo Hakim usey kuchh de to wo razi rahe warna khafa ho jaey. teesrey wo shakhs jo apna ( bechney ka ( saman Asr ke baad lekar khada hua aur kehney laga ke us Allah ki qism jiske siwa koi sachcha maabood nahi, mujhey us saman ki qeemat itni itnii mil rahi thi, is par aik shakhs ne usey sach samjha (aur uski batai hui qeemat par us saman ko khareed liya ( phir aap ne us aayat ki tilawat ki) إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ( ''jo log Allah ko darmyan mein de kar aur jhooti qismein kha kar duniya ka thoda sa maal mol letey hain'' aakhir tak."
2359,"aik Ansari mard ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se Harra ke naley mein jiska pani Madina ke log khajoor ke darakhton ko diya kartey they, apne jhagdey ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya. Ansari Zuber se kehney laga pani ko aagey janey do, lekin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko us se inkar tha aur yahi jhagdaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke (pahley apna baagh ( seench ley phir apne padosi bhai ke liye jaldi janey de. is par Ansari ko ghussa aa gaya aur unhon-ne kaha, haan Zuber aap ki phoophii ke ladkey hain naa . bas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak ka rang badal gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey Zuber ! tum sairaab kar lo, phir pani ko itni der tak rokey rakho ke wo mundeeron tak chadh jaey. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Allah ki qism ! mera to khayal hai ke ye aayat ( فلا وربك لا يؤمنون حتى يحكموك فيما شجر بينهم ) usi silsile mein nazil hui hai'' hargiz nahi, terey rab ki qism ! ye log us waqt tak momin nahi ho saktey jab tak apne jhagdon mein tujh ko Hakim na taslim kar lein '' aakhir tak."
2360,"aik Ansari mard ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se Harra ke naley mein jiska pani Madina ke log khajoor ke darakhton ko diya kartey they, apne jhagdey ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya. Ansari Zuber se kehney laga pani ko aagey janey do, lekin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko us se inkar tha aur yahi jhagdaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke (pahley apna baagh ( seench ley phir apne padosi bhai ke liye jaldi janey de. is par Ansari ko ghussa aa gaya aur unhon-ne kaha, haan Zuber aap ki phoophii ke ladkey hain naa . bas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak ka rang badal gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey Zuber ! tum sairaab kar lo, phir pani ko itni der tak rokey rakho ke wo mundeeron tak chadh jaey. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Allah ki qism ! mera to khayal hai ke ye aayat ( فلا وربك لا يؤمنون حتى يحكموك فيما شجر بينهم ) usi silsile mein nazil hui hai'' hargiz nahi, terey rab ki qism ! ye log us waqt tak momin nahi ho saktey jab tak apne jhagdon mein tujh ko Hakim na taslim kar lein '' aakhir tak."
2361,"Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se aik Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ka jhagdaa hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Zuber ! pahley tum ( apna baagh ( sairaab kar lo, phir pani aagey ke liye chhod denaa, is par Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye aap ki phoophii ke ladkey hain ! ye sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Zuber ! apna baagh itna sairaab kar lo ke pani uski mundeeron tak pahunch jaey itney rok rakho, Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mera guman hai ke ye aayat ( فلا وربك لا يؤمنون حتى يحكموك فيما شجر بينهم ) '' hargiz nahi, terey rab ki qism ! ye log us waqt tak momin nahi hongey jab tak aapko apne tamam ikhtalaafaat mein hukm na taslim kar lein. '' usi silsile mein nazil hui."
2362,"aik Ansari mard ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se Harra ke nadi ke barey mein jis se khajooron ke baagh sairaab hua kartey they, jhagdaa kya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Zuber ! tum sairaab kar lo. phir apne padosi bhai ke liye jald pani chhod dena. is par Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ji haan ! aap ki phoophii ke betey hain naa ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka rang badal gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Zuber ! tum sairaab karo, yahan tak ke pani khet ki mendon tak pahunch jaey. is tarah aap ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka pura haq dilva diya. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke qism Allah ki ye aayat usi barey mein nazil hui thi ( فلا وربك لا يؤمنون حتى يحكموك فيما شجر بينهم ) '' hargiz nahi, terey rab ki qism ! us waqt tak ye eman waley nahi hongey jab tak apne jumla ikhtalaafaat mein aapko hukm na taslim kar lein. '' ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke Ansar aur tamam logon ne iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad ki bina par ke '' sairaab karo aur phir us waqt tak ruk jao, jab tak pani mundeeron tak na pahunch jaaey.'' aik andaza laga liya, yani pani takhnon tak bhar jaey."
2363,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik shakhs ja raha tha ke usey sakht piyaas lagi , us ne aik kuwein mein utar kar pani piyaa . phir bahar aaya to dekha ke aik kutta haanp raha hai aur piyaas ki wjah se keechad chaat raha hai. us ne (apne dil mein) kaha, ye bhi us waqt aisi hi piyaas mein mubtala hai jaisey abhi mujhey lagi hui thi. ( chunanche wo phir kuwein mein utra aur) apne chamdey ke mozey ko) pani se) bhar kar usey apne munh se pakdey huey uper aaya, aur kuttey ko pani pilaya . Allah Taala ne iske us kaam ko qabool kya aur uski maghfirat farmai . sahaba ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! kya hamein chaupaaon par bhi ajr milega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, har jaandaar mein sawab hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Hammaad-bin-Salma aur Rabe-bin-Muslim ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se ki hai."
2364,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik baar suraj girahan ki Namaz padhi phir farmaya ( abhi abhii ( dozakh mujh se itni qareeb aa gaee thi ke maine chaunk kar kaha, aey rab! kya main bhi unhein mein se hun. itney mein dozakh mein meri nazar aik aurat par padi .) Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ( mujhey yad hai ke (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke) us aurat ko aik billi nooch rahi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum kya ke is par us azab ki kya wjah hai? aap ke sath waley farishton ne kaha ke us aurat ne us billi ko itni der tak baandhey rakha ke wo bhook ke maarey mar gaee."
2365,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik aurat ko azaab, aik billi ki wjah se hua jisey usne itni der tak baandhey rakha tha ke wo bhook ki wjah se mar gaee. aur wo aurat usi wjah se dozakh mein dakhil hui. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne us se farmaya tha aur Allah Taala hi zyada jaanney wala hai ke jab tu ney us billi ko baandhey rakha us waqt tak na to ney isey khilaaya na pilaya aur na chhoda ke wo zameen ke keedey makodey hi kha kar apna pet bhar leti ."
2366,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik piyala pesh kya gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey nosh farmaya, aap ki daain taraf aik ladka tha jo haaziriin mein sabse kam Umr tha. badi umr waley sahaba aap ki baain taraf they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey ladkey ! kya tumhari ijazat hai ke main us pyaley ka bacha hua pani boodhon ko dun? us ne jawab diya, ya Rasulullah ! main to aap ka jhoota apne hissey ka kisi ko dene wala nahi hun. aakhir aap ne wo piyala usi ko de diya."
2367,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, us zaat ki qism ! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. main (qiyamat ke din) apne hauz se kuchh logon ko is tarah haank doonga jaisey ajnabii oont hauz se haank diye jatey hain."
2368,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida ( Hajra (as) ( par Allah raham farmaai ke agar unhon-ne zamzam ko chhod diya hota, ya yun farmaya ke agar wo zamzam se chalo bhar bhar kar na letin to wo aik bahtaa chashma hota. phir jab qabila جرہم ke log aaey aur) Hajra (as) se) kaha ke aap hamein apne padaus mein qiyam ki ijazat dein to unhon-ne usey qabool kar liya us shart par ke pani par unka koi haq na hoga. qabila walon ne ye shart maan li thi."
2369,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya teen tarah ke aadmi aisey hain jin se qiyamat ke din Allah Taala baat bhi na karega aur na unki taraf nazar utha ke dekhega . wo shakhs jo kisi saman ke mutaalliq qism khaaey ke usey uski qeemat us se zyada di ja rahi thi jitni ab di ja rahi hai halanke wo jhoota hai. wo shakhs jisne jhooti qism Asr ke baad isliye khaaii ke iske zariey aik musalman ke maal ko Hazam kar jaey. wo shakhs jo apni zarurat se bachchey pani se kisi ko rokey . Allah Taala farmaeyga ke aaj main apna Fazal isi tarah tumhen nahi doonga jis tarah tum ne aik aisi cheez ke faaltu hissey ko nahi diya tha jisey khud tumharey hathon ne banaya bhi na tha. Ali ne kaha ke ham se Sufiyan ne Amr se kai martaba bayan kya ke unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se suna aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak us hadis ki sanad pahunchaatey they.
2370,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, charaagaah Allah aur uska rasool hi mehfooz kar sakta hai. ( ibne-Shahab ne) bayan kya ke ham tak ye bhi pahuncha hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne naqeea' mein charaagaah banwaai thi aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Saraf aur Rabza ko charaagaah banaya."
2371,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ghoda aik shakhs ke liye baais-e-sawaab hai, doosrey ke liye bachao hai aur teesrey ke liye wabaal hai. jiske liye ghoda ajr w sawab hai, wo wo shakhs hai jo Allah ki raah ke liye usko paaley , wo usey kisi hariyaaley maidan mein baandhey ( rawi ne kaha (ya kisi baagh mein. to jis qadr bhi wo us hariyaaley maidan mein ya baagh mein charey ga . uski nekiyon mein likha jaeyga agar ittifaq se uski rassii toot gaee aur ghoda aik ya 2 martaba aagey ke paon utha kar kooda to iske aasaar qadam aur leed bhi Malik ki nekiyon mein likhe jaeinge aur agar wo ghoda kisi nadi se guzrey aur iska pani piey chahe Malik ne usey pilaaney ka irada na kya ho to bhi ye uski nekiyon mein likha jaeyga to us niyat se paalaa janey vaala ghoda unhein wajhon se baais-e-sawaab hai. doosra shakhs wo hai jo logon se be-niyaaz rehney aur unke samney hath phailane se bchney ke liye ghoda paaley , phir uski gardan aur uski peeth ke silsile mein Allah Taala ke haq ko bhi faraamosh na karey to ye ghoda apne Malik ke liye parda hai. tesraa shakhs wo hai jo ghodey ko fakhr , dikhawey aur musalmanon ki dushmanii mein paaley . to ye ghoda uske liye wabaal hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se gadhon ke mutaalliq malum kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey iske mutaalliq koi hukm wahi se malum nahi hua. siwa us jaame aayat ke) من يعمل مثقال ذرة خيرا يره * ومن يعمل مثقال ذرة شرا يره ( ''jo shakhs zarra barabar bhi neki karega, iska badla paaeyga aur jo zarra barabar burai karega iska badla paaeyga .''"
2372,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik shakhs aaya aur aap se luqta ( rastey mein kisi ki gum hui cheez jo pa gaee ho (ke mutaalliq puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski thaili aur uske bandhan ki khub jaanch kar lo. phir aik saal tak iska elaan kartey raho. us waqt mein agar iska Malik aa jaey ( to usey de do ( warna phir wo cheez tumhari hai. saail ne poochha, aur gumshuda bakri ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, wo tumhari hai ya tumharey bhai ki hai ya phir bhediye ki hai. saail ne puchha aur gumshuda oont ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tumhen us se kya matlab ? uske sath usey sairaab rakhney wali cheez hai aur uska ghar hai, pani par bhi wo ja sakta hai aur darakht (ke patey ( bhi kha sakta hai yahan tak ke iska Malik usko pa jaey."
2373,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar koi shakhs rassii lekar lakdiyon ka ghataa laaey, phir usey bechey aur is tarah Allah Taala uski aabroo mehfooz rakhey to ye us se behtar hai ke wo logon ke samney hath phailaey aur) bheek ( usey di jaey ya na di jaey. uski bhi koi ummeed na ho."
2374,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar koi shakhs lakdiyon ka gathaa apni peeth par (bechney ke liye) liye phirey to wo us se achchha hai ke kisi ke samney hath phailaaey, phir chahe usey kuchh de ya na de."
2375,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath badr ki ladai ke mauqe par mujhey aik jawan ontni ghaneemat mein mili thi aur aik dusri ontni mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inayat farmai thi. aik din aik Ansari sahabi ke darwazey par main un donon ko us khayal se baandhey huey tha ke unki peeth par izkhir (arab ki aik khushboodaar ghaas jisey sunaar wghaira istemal kartey they) rakh kar bechney ley jaaunga. bani qainuqaa' ka aik sunaar bhi mere sath tha. is tarah (khayaal ye tha ke) uski aamadni se Fatima (Raziallahu anha) (jin se main nikah karne wala tha un) ka walima karunga. Hamza-bin-Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) usi (ansaarii ke) ghar mein sharab pi rahe they. unke sath aik gaaney wali bhi thi. us ne jab ye misra'a padha : ''haan : aey Hamza! utho, farba jawan oontniyon ki taraf'' ( badh ( Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) josh mein talwaar lekar uthey aur donon oontniyon ke kohan cheer diye. unke pet phaad daley aur unki kalejii nikal li (ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya ke) maine ibne-Shahab se poochha, kya kohan ka gosht bhi kaat liya tha. to unhon-ne bayan kya ke un donon ke kohan kaat liye aur unhein ley gaey. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, mujhey ye dekh kar badi takleef hui. phir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. aap ki khidmat mein us waqt Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they. maine aapko us waaqie ki itlaa di to aap tashrif laey. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath hi they aur main bhi aap ke sath tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas pahunchey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne narazgi zahir farmai to Hamza ne nazar utha kar kahaa'' tum sab mere bap-dada ke ghulam ho.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ultey paon lot kar unke paas se chaley aaey. ye sharab ki hurmat se pahley ka qissa hai."
2376,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bahrain mein zameen ka kuchh hissey bataur jaageer (ansaar ko) dene ka irada kya to Ansar ne arz kya ke ham jab lengey ke aap hamarey muhajir bhaiyon ko bhi isi tarah ke zameen ke hissey inayat farmaaein. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere baad (doosrey logon ko) tum par tarjeeh di jaya karegi to us waqt tum sabr karnaa, yahan tak ke ham se (aakhirat mein aa kar) mulaqat karo."
2377,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ko bula kar Bahrain mein zameen ka kuchchh hissey bataur jaageer deeni chahi to unhon-ne arz kya ke aey Allah ke rasool! agar aapko aisa karna hi hai to hamarey bhai Quraish (muhaajireen) ko bhi isi tarah ki hissey ki sanad likh dijiye. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas itni zameen hi na thi isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya'' mere baad tum dekhogey ke doosrey logon ko tum par muqaddam kya jaeyga to us waqt tum mujh se milney tak sabr kiye rahnaa.''
2378,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, oont ka haq ye hai ke unka doodh pani ke paas dohaa jaey."
2379,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke pewandkaarii ke baad agar kisi shakhs ne apna khajoor ka darakht bechaa to (is saal ki fasl ka ( phal bechney waley hi ka rehta hai. haan agar khareedaar shart laga de (ke phal bhi khareedaar hi ka hoga) to ye sura alag hai. aur agar kisi shakhs ne koi maal wala ghulam bechaa to wo maal bechney waley ka hota hai. haan agar khareedaar shart laga de to ye sura alag hai. ye hadis Imam Malik se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi marwi (bayan) hai is mein sirf ghulam ka zikr hai."
2380,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ariya ke silsile mein uski rukhsat di thi ke andaza karke khushk khajoor ke badley bechaa ja sakta hai.
2381,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mukhaahira, Muhaaqla aur Muzaabna se mana farmaya tha. isi tarah phal ko pukhta honey se pahley bechney se mana farmaya tha, aur ye ke mewa ya ghalla jo darakht par laga ho, Dinar w dirham hi ke badley bechaa jaey. albatta araayaa ki ijazat di hai."
2382,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sauda araayaa ki andaza karke khushk khajoor ke badley panch wasq se kam , ya (ye kaha ke) panch wasq ke andar ijazat di hai is mein shak Daawood-bin-Husain ko hua ( Sauda ariya ka bayan peechhey mufassal ho chuka hai)."
2383,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sauda Muzaabna yani darakht par lagey huey khajoor ko khushk ki hui khajoor ke badley bechney se mana farmaya, ariya karne walon ke ilawa ke unhein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat de di thi. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (rh)) ne kaha ke ibne-Ishaq ne kaha ke mujh se Bashir ne isi tarah ye hadis bayan ki thii."
2384,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sauda Muzaabna yani darakht par lagey huey khajoor ko khushk ki hui khajoor ke badley bechney se mana farmaya, ariya karne walon ke ilawa ke unhein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat de di thi. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke ibne-Ishaq ne kaha ke mujh se Bashir ne isi tarah ye hadis bayan ki thii."
